From the course embedded
operating system and

44
00:03:08.180 --> 00:03:13.910
hardware, you will apply your skills for
planning the embedded hardware platform.

45
00:03:13.910 --> 00:03:18.480
Planning the performance required for
the processing, the cost of building such

46
00:03:18.480 --> 00:03:23.390
system and
the energy such a system would consume.

47
00:03:23.390 --> 00:03:28.470
You will need to program a lot in this
course and most of the programming

48
00:03:28.470 --> 00:03:33.582
will be based on the course
development of realtime systems.

49
00:03:33.582 --> 00:03:38.400
The realtime processing of system must
match the system requirements and

50
