correct scheduling must be ensured.

51
00:03:41.530 --> 00:03:47.840
Finally, you will need to utilize your
skills from course web connectivity and

52
00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:52.630
security in embedded systems to
establish the web connectivity and

53
00:03:52.630 --> 00:03:55.750
ensure the secure transfer
of data to the Cloud server.

